<h1>GearSmith Guides</h1>
<p>Welcome! GearSmith helps you track vehicle maintenance, service history, and repairs.</p>

<section>
<h2>Getting Started</h2>
<ul>
<li>Add your vehicles to the app.</li>
<li>Set up maintenance schedules (oil changes, tire rotations, etc.).</li>
<li>Enable reminders for upcoming service.</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Logging Maintenance</h2>
<ul>
<li>Open a vehicle profile.</li>
<li>Click "Add Service" and fill in details (date, type, cost, notes).</li>
<li>Attach receipts or photos if needed.</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Viewing Service History</h2>
<ul>
<li>Open the vehicle profile.</li>
<li>Scroll through service records.</li>
<li>Use filters to find specific entries.</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Back to Guides</h2>
